### Trace a Single Record Back to Its Raw Table

This is the most surgical check. Take one parsed record and find the exact original log it came from.

**Step 1 — Grab one record and note its key fields:**

```kusto
_Im_Dns()
| take 1
| project TimeGenerated, SrcIpAddr, DnsQuery, _ResourceId, EventProduct, EventVendor
```

**Step 2 — Use the ResourceId and timestamp to find the raw record:**

```kusto
// Paste the _ResourceId value from above into this query
// Adjust the timestamps to be 1 minute before and after the TimeGenerated value you saw
AzureDiagnostics
| where _ResourceId == "PASTE_RESOURCE_ID_HERE"
| where TimeGenerated between (datetime(PASTE_TIMESTAMP_MINUS_1MIN) .. datetime(PASTE_TIMESTAMP_PLUS_1MIN))
| take 5
